casebody.data:
LINH THI MINH TRAN, Petitioner,
v.
STAN THE HOT WATER MAN. No. 19-6285. Supreme Court of the United States. Jan. 13, 2020.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Oregon dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
